original: Mellberg, Sven Gustaf Adolf, kyrkoherde, Salstad, f. 9/12/94 i Larv, Skarab. k, av Sven Erland M. o. Klara Andersdotter. G. 25 m. Agnes Hæ-germarck. Barn i Per Gustaf f. 25, Agnes Elisabet 27, Sara Margareta 30. — Studiex. i Upps. 19, teol. fil. ex. 21, teok kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Skara stift 24. Tjg. i Källby 24, kommin. i Hassle s. å., i Kvänum 29, kyrkoh. i Flo, As o. Sal sed. 35.
translated: Mellberg, Sven Gustaf Adolf, clergyman, Salstad, b. 9/12/94 in Larv, Skaraborg county, son of Sven Erland M. and Klara Andersdotter. Married on 25 to Agnes Hægermarck. Children: Per Gustaf b. 25, Agnes Elisabet b. 27, Sara Margareta b. 30. – Graduated from Uppsala University in 19, with a degree in theology in 21, completed practical theology exams and ordained as a priest for the Skara diocese in 24. Served in Källby in 24, as an assistant clergyman in Hassle in the same year, in Kvänum in 29, and as a parish priest in Flo, As, and Sal from 35 onwards.
